    Plastic ageing analysis
1) Get vertical tracks and corresponding hits from digi files.
    danss_submit run_digi_mpi run_begin run_end
2) Calculate average 1 pixel integrals for all strips.
    ./f1px_avr file_with_1px_average.bin [run_begin run_end]
File name avr1px.bin is expected at the next step.
3) Run phe_hist to create medians etc.
    ./phe_hist result_file.root run_begin run_end chunk_size alpha [cuts]
